Definition: of textures that are smooth to the touch or substances consisting of relatively small particles
Example: wood with a fine grain; fine powdery snow; fine rain; batiste is a cotton fabric with a fine weave; covered with a fine film of dust
Synonyms: noun, attribute, fineness, COARSE, SMOOTH, texture, of, textures, that, are, smooth, to, the, touch, or, substances, consisting, relatively, small, particles, wood, with, a, fine, grain, powdery, snow, rain, batiste, is, cotton, fabric, weave, covered, film, dust
Category: adj.all
